          <p><a href="ch67.html#MonstersH-I10">Green hags</a> are found in desolate swamps and dark forests.<a href="img/MonstersH-I.Green_Hag.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersH-I.Green_Hag.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
          <p>A <a href="ch67.html#MonstersH-I10">green hag</a> is about the same height and weight as a female human.</p>
          <div class="sect4" lang="en">
            <div class="titlepage">
